  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChanceGiving
    ChanceGiving is the class of a magical ability which , increases the chances of the player immediately.
    DoubleAccel
    DoubleAccel is the class of an adversary magical ability which halves the speed of the enchanted sphere for 15 seconds.
    HollowPurple
    HollowPurple is the class of an adversary magical ability which creates 8 HollowPurpleObstacle objects and locates them randomly on the game when it is activated.
    InfiniteVoid
    InfiniteVoid is the class of an adversary magic which freezes random 8 obstacles on the game for 15 seconds.
    MagicalHex
    MegicalHex is the class of a magical ability which provides the noble phantasm to fire magical hexes and shoots the obstacles.
    NoblePhantasmExpansion
    NoblePhantasmExpansion is the class of a magical ability which doubles the length of the noble phantasm for 30 seconds when it is activated.
    UnstoppableEnchantedSphere
    UnstoppableEnchantedSphere is the class of a magical ability which provides the sphere the power of destructing the obstacles without reflecting back for 30 seconds when it is activated.
